{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A tag is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users quickly find, group, or understand content."}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV","title":"OUDSTag","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"symbolKind":"struct","modules":[{"name":"Components"}]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Appearances","type":"heading","text":"Appearances"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"emphasized","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"primary or high-priority information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"muted"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Status","type":"heading","text":"Status"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Neutral","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status needs to be communicated."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"completed actions or approved items."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Warning","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requiring user awareness or intervention.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Negative","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"problems or failed actions."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info"}]},{"text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or contextual information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Disabled","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allowed when loader is activated."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Shape","type":"heading","text":"Shape"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two shapes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Rounded","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Square"}]},{"text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Size","type":"heading","text":"Size"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two sizes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Default"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Small"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when grouping elements visually."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Layout","type":"heading","text":"Layout"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are four available layouts for tags:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text only","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"elements.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Bullet","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Icon","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as status, type, or action."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Loader","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress."}]}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-syst